---
title: Marvelous No-Bake Peanut Butter Mousse as an extra Serves 2
description: A peanut lover's dream awaits with tonight's no-bake peanut butter mousse! Cream cheese, peanut butter, sugar and heavy creamy whip together into a glorious fluffy dessert topped with crunchy chopped peanuts and a decadent chocolate drizzle!
